high_descs: Turn to the left, head to the white kitchen table
Take the butter knife from the table
Take a few steps to the right
Put the butter knife in the black mug
Take the black mug from the table
Turn to the left, head to the black table next to the white table in the corner
put the black mug on the corner table
anns.task_desc: Put the butter knife in the black mug, put the black mug on the black table

high_descs: Turn to the left, and then the right to find the white table.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the table.
Take a step to the right.
Place the knife inside a cup in the middle of the table.
Pick up the cup from the table.
Carry the cup and move a few steps to the left.
Place the cup and knife on the right side of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and knife to a table.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the door and walk to the white table.
Pick up the knife to the left of the tomato on the table.
Turn right and face left just before the loaf of bread on the table.
Put the knife inside the black glass behind the tomato.
Pick up the black glass with the knife inside.
Turn left, hang a left at the door, and turn around to face the small black table.
Place the black glass with the knife behind the spatula on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass and a knife on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward, turn right and walk toward the white table.
Pick up the knife from the table to the left of the tomato.
Turn right, walk forward, then turn left to face the middle of the white table.
Place the knife in the cup.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn left, walk towards the wall, turn left again, step forward, then turn all the way around to face the black shelf.
Place the cup with the knife in it on the top of the black shelf behind the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it on the black shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room to the white door, turn right and go to the white table.
Pick up the knife to the left of the tomato.
Turn right, head towards the loaf of bread on your left, turn left before you reach it to face a spoon on the white table.
Put the knife inside the black cup to the left of the spoon on the table.
Pick up the black cup with the knife inside of it.
Turn left, go to the white wall near the door ahead, and turn around to face a small black table.
Place the black cup with the knife inside on the black table to the right side behind the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife inside a cup on to the table.

high_descs: Go forward and left to the left side of the white table.
Pick up the butter knife.
Take a step right.
Put the butter knife in the black cup.
Pick up the cup.
Step to the left.
Put the cup on the back table behind the spatuala.
anns.task_desc: Put a black mug with a fork in it on a table.
